Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:01.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darkness and Light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.90,0:00:03.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Into the chaos of\nthe Feudal Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:05.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel brings a\n{\i1}group of strangers together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:09.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}500 years across time,\ntheir destinies are controlled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.14,0:00:11.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the few remaining shards\nof the Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.91,0:00:13.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feudal Fairy Tale:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:14.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:17.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo turned out to be\NSt. Hijiri, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:21.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}As I pursued the Soul Collectors,\NI came upon Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:24.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo, are you alive?\NOr...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:16.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are they telling me\nto follow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:23.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:26.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A {\i1}waterfall....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:29.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:36.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:02:59.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone was dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:00.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:03.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone who was\nin the birthing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:07.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,According to the men\nwho found them the following morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:09.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,there was something\nvery strange about their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:12.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Was it the work\nof demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:14.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:20.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it is a blessing that our\nlady and her newborn were unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:23.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Buddha must have protected them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:28.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A fine {\i1}babe....{\i0} a fine babe indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:30.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My {\i1}lord....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:32.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:33.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:35.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:37.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:39.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Security has been tightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:43.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon or whatever, it will not\nget near this castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:47.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I finally have an heir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:50.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall protect him\nwith my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:55.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that babe really mine?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:03:59.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That white child...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was she just an illusion?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:04.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:16.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for the trouble, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:17.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's no trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:20.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hate growing old!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:26.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Spraining my back carrying\n{\i1}firewood....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:27.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:29.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mustn't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:32.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's your name, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:33.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:35.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your {\i1}name....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:37.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you have a place\nto stay tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then come to my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At least I can offer\nyou something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:48.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:51.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My name's Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:54.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku?\NThat's a fancy name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:56.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:07.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:15.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, I think that's the last\nof them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:21.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara, you did great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:25.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are there more left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:32.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So there were demons\nhere, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's only Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:35.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't scare us like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:37.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey....where's Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:39.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:43.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome went after\nthe Soul Collectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:45.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Soul Collectors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:48.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And she just....disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:51.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was probably a barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:53.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's this barrier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:54.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take me there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:07.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:08.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:11.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Her life is fading.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:14.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The miasma is spreading.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:15.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miasma?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:20.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please {\i1}choose....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:22.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whether you will save her\nor not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you {\i1}mean....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:27.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"choose"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:29.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's happening to Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:31.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After Mt. Hakurei was destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:34.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,she was struck by one of\NNaraku's tentacles
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:37.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and fell into a dark river\nof miasma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:42.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But because her body was made\nof sacred bones and dirt from her grave,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the miasma could not dissolve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:45.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:50.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the miasma that entered through\nher wounds spread throughout her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:52.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The wound in her chest still\nhas not healed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:54.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and the miasma is eating\naway her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:06:59.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The only one who can save {\i1}her....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:02.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:04.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}can save Kikyo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:06.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:09.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you hold this lady's life\nin your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:11.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So they're...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}telling me to choose?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:20.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What must I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What must I do to save her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.91,0:07:26.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You choose to save her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:27.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who can, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:31.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All you have to do is touch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:35.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the miasma will\nbe purified.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just touch her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:39.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:43.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Soul Transfer Doll has\nbeen broken
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:46.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and it is very difficult to\nhang on to her soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:49.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we don't purify the miasma\nbefore the sun sets,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:52.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,her soul will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:54.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:00.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This water hurts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku's miasma is oozing out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:11.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:18.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this the miasma that has\nseeped into the water?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:21.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is all this from Kikyo's body?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:25.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:26.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I need to take a look.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looks terrible...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:32.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You poor thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:40.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They said all I had to do\nwas touch her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:44.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What must I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:47.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What must I do\nto awaken Kikyo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:01.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:03.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:06.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is soil from her grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:09.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your hand purified it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:12.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please rub that into her wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:13.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:22.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The miasma is pushing out\nthe soil!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:29.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The power of the miasma grows\nstronger with the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:34.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must save her soul\nbefore the sun {\i1}sets....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:41.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}l- lt hurts so much...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:44.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel like I'm going to\nbe thrown backwards.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:49.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's pitch black...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:51.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't see a thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:58.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:00.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:02.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- I'm late!\N- {\i1}the Sacred Jewel?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:09.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- {\i1}So what I'm seeing...{\i0}\N- That {\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- {\i1}are scenes from before Kikyo died?{\i0}\N- Maybe he overslept.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:14.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Scenes from fifty years ago?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:24.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watch out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:33.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if you try to pretty\nyourself up with this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:35.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you can't hide your\ntrue nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:37.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:40.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This rouge doesn't become\nyou at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:44.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon blood is good\nenough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:47.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:49.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:54.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:56.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha would never\nsay such things!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:02.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I never wanted to become\na human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:04.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why don't you realize it?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:08.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks for the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:13.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll have to make it suck more\nblood filled with hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:15.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo! That's Naraku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:17.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll slaughter the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Curse {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:20.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can't you see?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:21.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:31.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She will not make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:33.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo's soul is fading away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:37.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:39.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is where Kagome disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:40.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:41.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where is she?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:11:59.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:02.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo's shoulder and chest\ninjuries...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:05.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}are the same as the\nones she has now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.93,0:12:08.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Curse you! Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:12.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:14.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:18.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I trusted you...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:21.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really trusted you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:23.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:35.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}K-Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:39.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:45.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister! Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:45.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:47.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen, {\i1}Kaede....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:52.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this Sacred Jewel and\nburn it with my {\i1}body....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:52.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:54.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- {\i1}That's what happened!{\i0}\N- so that it will never pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:56.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,into the hands of evil again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:58.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo's soul cannot get past\nthis moment in time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:02.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:04.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:08.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:13.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time stopped for Kikyo\nat this point.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? What happened to me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:25.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was I dreaming?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:30.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dream? But what kind of dream?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:32.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mind feels so muddled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:36.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:41.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The wounds are closing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:44.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just a little more!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:46.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hang in there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:54.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hang in there, Kikyo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:14:01.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha really wants to\nsee you again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:03.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So hang in there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inu....yasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:11.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Y- You can do it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:16.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You want to see Inuyasha, too...\NRight?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:19.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:30.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The water... is becoming clearer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:35.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The miasma has been purified!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:40.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so glad...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:58.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Soul {\i1}Collectors....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:14:59.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:04.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:12.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:13.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:16.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:19.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the one who called\nme here, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:22.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You had a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:25.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To save me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:30.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know, it really wasn't\na matter of choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:35.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If there's a person before me\nwhom I could {\i1}save....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:38.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I'm told that I'm the only one\nwho {\i1}can{\i0} save {\i1}her....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:39.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,naturally I would choose\nto save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:42.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:44.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:47.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Since you made the choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:48.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:54.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cripes, she's so difficult.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:58.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you see something\nwhile you were in the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:03.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you don't remember,\nso be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:06.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:10.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha will be here {\i1}soon....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:12.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iooking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:13.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:16.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will go into hiding\nfor a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:18.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must restore my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:22.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why won't you see Inuyasha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:25.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:27.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:34.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha has only had thoughts\nof you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:37.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}since hearing about\NSt. Hijiri...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:43.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are the one Inuyasha\nlongs for...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:45.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}even though that upsets me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:48.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This {\i1}sound....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:50.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:52.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:53.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A waterfall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:58.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us go! Perhaps the barrier\nis down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:16:59.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:12.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please choose whether...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:14.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}to save her or not.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:18.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Geez! Those two... talking like they\nwere testing me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:21.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet why did they?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:25.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could this have been\nabout Inuyasha?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:28.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did she think I wouldn't have saved\nher because she's in the way?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:31.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the only reason I\n{\i1}can think of.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's so belittling!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:37.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}How could they think\NI'm such an awful woman?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:39.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:42.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's all right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:47.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:48.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:49.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:54.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you looking around for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:17:59.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why don't you go after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:04.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, but she already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:08.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even though I told her to\nstay and see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:13.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it, he's happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:19.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, what'll you do?\NWill you go after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:27.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, did something\nhappen between you and Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:33.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I felt so determined back then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:36.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never thought I'd feel\nlike this now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:37.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, {\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:42.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey you! What's with your\nlong face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:43.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:43.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:47.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all your fault!\NI hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:48.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:50.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}K-Kagome....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:51.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She looks so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:55.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the hell did I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:58.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just cut it out 'cuz you're\nmaking me mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:18:59.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:03.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you think, Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:06.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened,\nbut it's probably Inuyasha's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:08.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After all, Kagome said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:14.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Apologize? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:16.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:20.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you ever seen\nher look so sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:22.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:26.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, let me ask you\none question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:30.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't you going after Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:34.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How can I with Kagome\nlooking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:39.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then if Kagome had sent you off\nwith a smile, you'd have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.14,0:19:39.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:49.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boy, I'm so awful!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:53.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was upset and took it all\nout on Inuyasha.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:55.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I've made him hate me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:19:58.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:01.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:04.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you still upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:06.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't you going after Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:15.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I was up there alone\nat the base of the {\i1}mountain....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I met St. Hijiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:21.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it turned out to be\na puppet of Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:27.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I learned that the real Kikyo was\novercome by Naraku's miasma
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:30.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and that her life was nearing its end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:33.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So he knew...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:38.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How {\i1}was....{\i0} Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:40.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She was hurt and asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:42.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:46.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was able to purify the miasma,\nso I think she'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:52.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:55.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:57.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's only natural...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:00.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}that he would be worried.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:06.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, go to her.\NDon't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:08.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not going!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:08.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:10.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the one who shouldn't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:12.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You saved Kikyo, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:13.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh-huh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:16.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then, she's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.41,0:21:17.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't go after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:20.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:21.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:26.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So take back what\nyou said earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.79,0:21:27.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:29.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't pretend you forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:31.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You told me you hated me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:34.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:34.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:37.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:40.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you realize how hurt\NI felt when you said that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:41.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So it did bother him, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:43.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So {\i1}sensitive....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:51.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There was no doubt\nin Kagome's heart...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:21:57.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If there had been, the wound\nin my chest would not have closed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:01.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It still feels warm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:47.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Around the time St. Hijiri appeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.49,0:23:50.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Princess Abi's mother noticed a spot\nwhich demons avoided.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:52.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will kill Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.23,0:23:54.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing good has come of\nmy involvement with him!
